{"tid":733771,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【七月新番】音樂少女","createTime":"2018-07-08T05:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T16:04:18.000Z","uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2cffdd481f1fa553788db014984ab49e7dec6a9d","tid":733771,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/131610_3a2549980e189f51ee90b48e72c47d04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F131610_3a2549980e189f51ee90b48e72c47d04.png&h=c16bc626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《音樂少女》故事描述 PINE RECORDS 共 11 人是名為「音樂少女」的偶像組合的成員，但卻是個完全紅不起來的偶像團體。為此製作人池橋和成員們都在努力著......<br />\n<br />\n-STAFF-<br />\n原作：SQUARE ENIX <br />\n監督：菅沼榮治 <br />\n系列構成：鈴木雅詞 <br />\n角色設計：川村敏江 <br />\n動畫製作：asread、tear-studio<br />\n<br />\n-CAST-<br />\n山田木花子：深川芹亞<br />\n箕作沙沙芽：高橋花林<br />\n西尾未來：岡咲美保<br />\n雪野日陽：大野柚布子<br />\n具志堅修普：島袋美由利<br />\n諸岡露露：江口菜子<br />\n等 ...<br />\n<br />\n-PV-<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwKl5uQE99g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGwKl5uQE99g&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f8e34ec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwKl5uQE99g</a><br />\n<br />\n-INFO-<br />\n放送日期：7 月 6 日 <br />\n每週更新：星期六</div>"},{"pid":"139532735def3000dc13dd02d925ae68870a3126","tid":733771,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/145707_36b16ac9095beefc9b46af0dacfb46e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F145707_36b16ac9095beefc9b46af0dacfb46e2.png&h=079a3433&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"147e6d8f01fe48458f3e27b23730a1cdbb146118","tid":733771,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,